  "decision_conditions": [
    "Reason : 1 - The proposed development, by virtue of its failure to provide marketing information, has failed to demonstrate that the loss of the office floorspace in this location should be considered appropriate. The proposed development is therefore contrary to Local Plan Policy ED2 (Maintaining the Borough's Employment Land Supply). ",
    "Reason : 2 - The proposed development, by virtue of its failure to include a flood risk assessment, has failed to demonstrate it would not be susceptible to flood risk or would not increase flood risk elsewhere. The proposed development is therefore contrary to Local Plan Policy EQ3 (Flood risk and surface water management) and the aims and principles of the National Planning Policy Framework (2023).",
    "Reason : 3 - The proposed development, by virtue of the under-provision of private amenity space would result inadequate external accommodation that fail to provide an acceptable standard of accommodation for future occupiers. The proposed development is therefore contrary to London Plan Policy D6 (Housing quality and standards) and Local Plan Policies CC2 (Urban design and architecture) and SC5 (Ensuring suitable internal and external space), the aims and principles of the National Planning Policy Framework (2023).",
    "Reason : 4 - The proposed development would fail to provide adequate access to cycle parking facilities for future occupiers, failing to sufficiently promote sustainable modes of transport, and would therefore fail to comply with Local Plan policy EC2 (Developing a sustainable local transport network) and London Plan policy T5 (Cycling)."
  ],
